divs: Sighting DetailsHi, I'm Abraham from Philippines. I'm just wondering if any one from your team can investigate this picture that I took about 3 weeks ago. Me and my friend just past by in this rice field near a volcano not to far away from our home, just now i realized there is something out there in the sky that is really weird. When i started browsing my photos from a holiday back in my homeland Philippines. I took this picture using my iPhone 4s so it's not really a high resolution, but attached is the raw file of this photo. Just send me your email address. Thank You.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Legaspi
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: It is a grayish metal, that is flying above the rice field near a Volcano called Mt. Mayon
